                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Re-examined</hi>). I know Mr. Philip by sight—I do not I know of his being in business, but I believe he has been to my office several times as the manager of Nicholle, Dupin, and Co.; that was after the 19th December.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner received an excellent character.</hi>
               </p>
